# Data & models — image data stays out of git (dataset licensing; Fitzpatrick17k is
# non-commercial). Images / raw CSVs / manifest / splits / QA reports are shared via
# the team Google Drive, not git. Licensing/provenance lives in docs/PROVENANCE.md.
# The only committable thing under data/ is the label crosswalk (non-image taxonomy).
# License-restricted data handoffs / manifests — must live on the team Drive, NOT here:
/dermaface-data-handoff/
/dermaface-manifests/
/DermaFace_Cleaned_Manifest.docx
*.REAL.csv
data/raw/*
data/processed/*
data/external/*
!data/**/.gitkeep
# Small config/map artifacts ARE tracked (they're rules, not data/PII):
!data/external/severity_map.csv
!data/external/label_map.csv
models/*
!models/.gitkeep
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.h5
*.onnx

